title: RHOBH: Lick My Aspen
description:
The Real Housewives of Beverly Hills finally heads to Aspen for its much hyped major cast trip of the season. Predictably, the first night culminates in the group ganging up on Sutton and Diana calling her a cut fitness. Great work, team!

Catch this recap on video with Crappens on Demand here: https://www.patreon.com/posts/71384532?pr=true
author: watchwhatcrappens@gmail.com (benron)
